OL,3,CTeenager takes on run for charity that
OL,4,Chelped him during cancer treatment
OL,6,FBarrie Wells and James Holcroft joined
OL,7,FMike Hall and Victoria Grimes in the
OL,8,FGranada Reports studio to talk about
OL,9,FJames' Great North Run challenge.
OL,11,FA teenager from Chorley is taking on
OL,12,Fthe Great North Run to raise money for
OL,13,Fa charity which helped him when he was
OL,14,Fundergoing treatment for cancer.
OL,16,FJames Holcroft was diagnosed with
OL,17,FAcute Lymphoblastic Leukemia when he
OL,18,Fwas just ten years old. He spent more
OL,19,Fthan a hundred days in hospital and
OL,20,Fendured many treatments, and also lost
OL,21,Fthe ability to walk.
