OL,3,CTeenager takes on run for charity that
OL,4,Chelped him during cancer treatment
OL,6,FJames, now 19, was helped by charity
OL,7,FBox4Kids, which invites seriously ill
OL,8,Fchildren and their families to enjoy
OL,9,FVIP experiences at iconic sporting and
OL,10,Fentertainment venues.
OL,12,FIt was started by businessman Barrie
OL,13,FWells, who began by using his own
OL,14,Fexecutive box at Anfield Stadium to
OL,15,Fprovide days out for seriously ill and
OL,16,Fdisabled children.
