OL,3,CTeenager takes on run for charity that
OL,4,Chelped him during cancer treatment
OL,6,FHe has now been given the all-clear
OL,7,Fand wants to repay the favour by
OL,8,Fraising money for Box4Kids and has
OL,9,Ffond memories of the days out he
OL,10,Fexperienced through the charity: "I
OL,11,Fhave some fantastic memories -
OL,12,FLiverpool Football Club, Sale sharks,
OL,13,FThe Jockey Club at Haydock races -
OL,14,Fmemories I'll have for life.
OL,16,F"It was a massive distraction from
OL,17,Fwhat I was going through - and it made
OL,18,Fme feel so special to experience a box
OL,19,F- I would never have dreamed of that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
