OL,3,CTeenager takes on run for charity that
OL,4,Chelped him during cancer treatment
OL,6,FBarrie said:" I was an entrepreneur
OL,7,Funtil 2008, but it felt like it was a
OL,8,Fvery selfish existence, so I thought
OL,9,FI'd give all my money away and I've
OL,10,Fbecome a philanthropist.
OL,12,F"It is the happiest time of my life, I
OL,13,Fget so much joy from seeing the
OL,14,Fchildren enjoying the events and James
OL,15,Fis such a special case. I remember him
OL,16,Fwhen he was 10, he was so ill and was
OL,17,Fhaving chemotherapy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
