OL,3,CTeenager takes on run for charity that
OL,4,Chelped him during cancer treatment
OL,6,F"Looking at him now, I can't believe
OL,7,Fthe change in him. I was quite
OL,8,Femotional when he told me he was going
OL,9,Fto do the Great North Run to raise
OL,10,Fmoney for Box4Kids."
OL,12,FJames will take on the 13 mile Great
OL,13,FNorth Run on Sunday 8th September.
